# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in all values before running any project locally.
**Never commit `.env` to Git.**

```dotenv
# ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Cloud – common
# ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Target GCP project ID (samantha-agent | nora-agent | sloane-agent)
GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=samantha-agent

# GCP region used for Cloud Run, Artifact Registry, Vertex AI, etc.
GOOGLE_CLOUD_REGION=us-central1

# Path to a service-account JSON key (leave blank to use ADC / gcloud auth)
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=

# ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Artifact Registry
# ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Full registry hostname  (format: REGION-docker.pkg.dev)
AR_REGISTRY=us-central1-docker.pkg.dev

# Artifact Registry repository name inside the project
AR_REPOSITORY=agents

# ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Cloud Run
# ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Name of the Cloud Run service to deploy / update
CLOUD_RUN_SERVICE=

# Maximum number of container instances
CLOUD_RUN_MAX_INSTANCES=10

# ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Vertex AI / Gemini
# ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Vertex AI endpoint region
VERTEX_AI_REGION=us-central1

# Model to use (e.g. gemini-1.5-pro, gemini-2.0-flash-exp)
VERTEX_AI_MODEL=gemini-1.5-pro

# ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Secret Manager
# ──────────────────────────────────────────

# GCP project that hosts secrets (often the same as GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT)
SECRET_MANAGER_PROJECT=

# ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Application-level settings
# ──────────────────────────────────────────

# Public-facing base URL of the agent service
AGENT_BASE_URL=

# Log level: DEBUG | INFO | WARNING | ERROR
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
```
